    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p>This Cookie Policy explains how NomadProHub uses cookies and similar technologies to recognize you when you visit our website.</p>
    <h2>What Are Cookies?</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small data files placed on your device when you visit a website. They help us improve your experience and analyze usage.</p>
    <h2>How We Use Cookies</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To remember your preferences</li>
      <li>To analyze site traffic</li>
      <li>To provide personalized content</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Session cookies (essential for site operation)</li>
      <li>Analytics cookies (Google Analytics, etc.)</li>
      <li>Preference cookies</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Third-Party Cookies</h2>
    <p>We may use third-party services that set cookies on your device. These include analytics providers and social media platforms.</p>
    <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>
    <p>You can manage your cookie preferences through our site settings or your browser settings.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:2em;font-size:0.95em;color:#888;">Last updated: August 10, 2025</p>
    <h2>Your Choices</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You can set your browser to refuse cookies or alert you when cookies are being sent.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Contact us at support@nomadprohub.com for more information.</p>
    <h2>User Definition</h2>
    <p>NomadProHub only has a registered admin or site owner. All other visitors are public viewers and do not have accounts or profiles.</p>
  </main>
